/* Empty file

   This file can be overridden to add extra memory regions.

   For example, to add a PSRAM region, you would replace
   this file with:

   MEMORY
   {
      PSRAM(rwx) : ORIGIN =  0x11000000, LENGTH = 8M
   }

   Or to include a XIP_RAM region, you would replace
   this file with:

   INCLUDE "memory_xip_ram.incl"
*/
